com.ibm.opencard.dictionary
Class Item

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.ibm.opencard.dictionary.Item
public class Item
extends java.lang.Object

Item represents an item entry contained in an AgentDictionary. Item objects are only instanciated by the itemEntry method of AgentDictionary (or derived classes).

See Also:
opencard.core.util.TLV, com.ibm.opencard.dictionary.AgentDictionary
